  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <l>TO make a Wife of wit, or meere Philosophie,</l>
   <l>And deck her vp with flowers of sweetest poesie,</l>
   <l>Is no hard taske, but such a one of flesh to find</l>
   <l>Would weary all the wits and bodies of mankind<hi>:</hi>
   </l>
   <l>Since worse must serue the turne, then men must bee con<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tent</l>
   <l>To take such as they find, not such as they invent.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>T. B.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
